<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.345274>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Irene gen. n. & Kollariana spp., adults. 1. I. litanga, male, holotype, China, Sichuan (coll. GBG / ZSM); 2. I. litanga, female, paratype, China, Sichuan (coll. AFM); 3. I. litanga, female, paratype, China, Yunnan (coll. HNHM); 4. I. litanga, female, paratype, China, Yunnan (coll. HNHM); 5. K. scotochlora, male, Pakistan, Kaghan valley (PGM); 6. K. scotochlora, female, Pakistan, Kaghan valley (PGM)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/345274/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.345277>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 22. Kollariana, Polia spp. & Bryoxena spp. male and female genitalia. 17. K. scotochlora, male, gen. prep. GYP 4442 m; 18. P. nebulosa, male, gen. prep. GYP 4447 m; 19. B. centralasiae, male, gen. prep. GYP 4449 m; 20. K. scotochlora, female, gen. prep. GYP 4445 f; 21. P. nebulosa, female, gen. prep. GYP 4439 f; 22. B. centralasiae, female, gen. prep. GYP 4447 f." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/345277/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.345275>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 12. Polia, Bryoxena & Hada spp., adults. 7. P. nebulosa, male, Armenia, David-Bek (coll. ASV); 8. P. nebulosa, female, Japan, Honshu (coll. ASV); 9. B. centralasiae, female, Tadjikistan, Gissar (coll. PGM); 10. H. fraterna, male, holotype, E. Tibet, Taba (coll. PGM / HNHM); 11. H. fraterna, male, China, Sichuan (coll. AFM); 12. H. fraterna, female, China, Sichuan (coll. AFM)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/345275/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.345276>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 16. Irene gen. n. & Hada spp., male and female genitalia. 13. I. litanga, male, holotype, gen. prep. OP 3364 m; 14. H. fraterna, male, gen. prep. GYP 1863 m; 15. I. litanga, female, paratype, gen. prep. OP 3365 f; 16. H. fraterna, female, gen. prep. GYP 4514 f." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/345276/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

